# Input

```html
<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Test</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Hello</h1>
</body>
</html>

```


# Options

```json
{
  "$schema": "../../../../../../packages/@biomejs/biome/configuration_schema.json",
  "html": {
    "formatter": {
      "trailingNewline": false
    }
  }
}
```

# Formatted

```html
<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Test</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>Hello</h1>
	</body>
</html>
```
